# Project Workflow

- There is no Jira process for this project.
- Use `NO-JIRA` for commits when a ticket prefix is needed.
- There is no separate test environment.
- There are no separate feature or release branches by default.
- Work happens on `main`, and pushing to `main` triggers the Vercel deployment.
- Do not block pushes or deployment waiting for a Jira ID, test-environment promotion, or branch selection unless the user explicitly requests a different flow.
